                "invention-title": [
                    "Cylindrical multilayer reforming hydrogen production device and reforming hydrogen production method",
                    "筒形多层重整制氢装置及重整制氢方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of reforming hydrogen production, in particular to a cylindrical multilayer reforming hydrogen production device which comprises an outer cylinder, a middle cylinder, an inner cylinder, a rotating shaft, a combustion system and an electric heater, and sealing plates are arranged at the two ends of the outer cylinder. The middle cylinder is arranged in the outer cylinder, a combustion cavity is formed between the outer cylinder and the middle cylinder, and a fuel gas inlet and a tail gas outlet are formed in the positions, corresponding to the combustion cavity, of the sealing plate. The combustion system is arranged in the combustion cavity. The two ends of the rotating shaft are rotationally mounted on the sealing plates; the inner cylinder is fixed on the rotating shaft and is arranged in the middle cylinder; a reaction chamber is arranged between the inner cylinder and the middle cylinder, and the plurality of separation nets are distributed at intervals to separate the reaction chamber into a plurality of layers of reaction sections. In addition, the invention also relates to a reforming hydrogen production method. According to the invention, the reforming catalyst is filled in a layered manner, so that the optimal utilization of the reforming catalyst can be realized, the reaction chamber rotates to drive the reforming catalyst to rub and collide with each other, deposited carbon attached to the reforming catalyst can be effectively removed, and efficient utilization of energy is realized through multiple heat supply modes."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及重整制氢技术领域，具体涉及一种筒形多层重整制氢装置，其包括外筒、中筒、内筒、旋转轴、燃烧系统和电加热器，其中，外筒的两端均设置有封板。中筒设置于外筒内，外筒与中筒之间为燃烧腔，封板上对应燃烧腔的位置开设有燃料气入口和尾气出口；燃烧系统设置于燃烧腔内。旋转轴的两端均转动安装于封板上；内筒固定于旋转轴上且设置于中筒内。内筒与中筒之间为反应室，多个分隔网间隔分布将反应室分隔成多层反应段。另外，本发明还涉及一种重整制氢方法。本发明将重整催化剂进行分层装填，可以实现重整催化剂的最优利用，反应室旋转带动重整催化剂相互摩擦碰撞，可有效清除重整催化剂附着的积碳，而多种供热方式实现了能量的高效利用。"
                }
            ]
